{"tid":2438273,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"百老匯戲院遭建築公司入稟 追逾1133萬元建築費","createTime":"2021-03-08T11:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T12:46:13.000Z","uid":134993,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"01d91bece0139f13a4a2139cbe9ef23976d86d11","tid":2438273,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:27:04.000Z","msg":"入稟狀指，原告及兩名被告在2017年3月20日就興建在太古城中心( Cityplaza) 的百老匯戲院簽約，原告完成提供專業建築服務後，被告需在2019年8月16日或之前向原告支付逾$1183萬元的費用，但被告一直未有支付，直到2020年8月4日，被告提出分八期歸還所有費用，但被告在2020年11月2日向原告支付50萬元後便沒有再還款，原告指被告違約，被告現仍欠原告逾1133萬元，故入稟興訟連本帶利追討。"},{"pid":"852ae760d41678c6639bc10ce7de20ca92f8004c","tid":2438273,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:29:16.000Z","msg":"百老匯戲院 下一間"},{"pid":"0f76ea6763504ce10d9d33c76d50d287da20ef89","tid":2438273,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64f2c74873d2d638dbb5bee8bc803dc69be8b0a","tid":2438273,"uid":71433,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為大公司就唔會走數"},{"pid":"22d318db2524693fe40c352032fc14a87c57405d","tid":2438273,"uid":215228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a64f2c74873d2d638dbb5bee8bc803dc69be8b0a","tid":2438273,"uid":71433,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為大公司就唔會走數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大公司先最鐘意<br />\n平時都已經拖數拖<br />\n到最後走埋數"},{"pid":"fb9ce0e40e375b78c3021bdced312d091e388a6b","tid":2438273,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit